        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You imbue the target berry with the bounty of nature, turning it into a goodberry that can heal and sustain far beyond its normal capacity. A creature can eat the goodberry with an Interact action to regain 1d6+4 Hit Points. A berry not consumed during the duration withers away. Every six goodberries consumed gives as much nourishment as one square meal for a typical human.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spell-effects.Item.Spell Effect: Goodberry]</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> You can target an additional berry. A creature can consume any number of goodberries from the same casting with a single Interact action.</p>\n<p>[[/r (@item.level)d6+(@item.level)*4[positive]]]{Consume All Berries}</p>"
